This is the core function library
lib.php is called to load all the necessary funcitons.

calling lib.php does the following

1) starts the session
2) load DB Class
3) load functions
	3.1) load functions.php
		3.1.1) Load all functions.* files from both lib and user/lib
		3.1.2) Loads addons
4) logs the user in (yes, every time!)
5) offers the termination function for this library